videos.description: Jordy Tshimanga receives the pass and drives to the hoop for the power jam to give the Cornhuskers a 7-4 lead
videos.headline: Nebraska's Tshimanga powers it home

videos.description: Miles Bridges blocks the shot on one end, leads the break and finishes with a tip in as the Spartans take an 18-13 lead
videos.headline: Bridges owns both ends of the court

videos.description: Cassius Winston feeds Nick Ward down load for the dunk
videos.headline: MSU's Ward finishes strong

videos.description: Miles Bridges hits the 3 from the top of the key after Wisconsin pulled within 2 points
videos.headline: Bridges quiets crowd after draining 3
Tyronn Lue has his number retired during Michigan State v Nebraska game

videos.description: Cassius Winston drains the 3 to give MSU a 50-38 lead.
videos.headline: Spartans open up double digit lead

videos.description: Miles Bridges drives the baseline and finishes with the up and under as the Spartans take a 62-48 lead.
videos.headline: Bridges with beautiful baseline drive
